        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2457917425" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2722325524355209829">Excellent and inspiring book. The only downside is the second to last chapter when the Dalai Lama talks about all the things in the modern world that people are doing which give him hope. Most of those things are either falling apart or being torn apart now. There was still hope in 1999. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


